     >	trimmed length= 	 25
     > xxxxx   xxxxx   xxxxx
     > xxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
     >	untrimmed length=	     30 	 13
     >	trimmed length= 	     25 	 13
     >	sum trimmed length=	     38


